{
  "text": "Nevertheless, the current results are comparable to more traditional feature based classification methods [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . This demonstrates that multidimensional persistence is viable candidate for integration with other methods of developing features in radiological data. In particular, our methods may be complementary to the standard techniques currently in use.",
  "correct_citation": {
